response.original_title: Chikara Young Lions Cup VII - Night 3
response.overview: August 16th, 2009 :: The winners of the first two nights meet in the finals of the annual Young Lions Cup tournament! Tension escalates between Claudio Castagnoli and Eddie Kingston. Nine former Young Lions Cup Champions do battle in a once-in-a-lifetime “Golden Dream Triangle Trios” match! Matches featured:  1. SeaDonsters & Cloudy vs Yellow Dog, Player Uno & Dasher Hatfield  2. The Roughnecks vs The North Star Express  3. 4 Corner Elimination: F.I.S.T. vs The Colony vs The Order of the Neo-Solar Temple vs Chiva V, Halcon Guerrero  4. Pierrothito vs Mascarita Dorado  5. Turbo & Frightmare vs Mike Quackenbush & Jorge "Skayde" Rivera  6. Eddie Kingston vs Claudio Castagnoli  7. Golden Dream: The UnStable & Chuck Taylor vs The Future Is Now vs Fire Ant, Arik Cannon & Hallowicked  8. Young Lions Cup Tournament Finals
response.title: Chikara Young Lions Cup VII - Night 3
